    {
      "type": "accordion",
      "title": "Recommended Acts",
      "subtitle": "Commonly recommended for practising on 15th Shaaban Eve and Day",
      "items": [
        {
          "title": "General Acts",
          "color": "emerald",
          "content": "<b>Stay awake during the night</b><br>Whoever stays up on the night of the Eid and the middle night of Shaban to worship, his heart shall not perish on the day all hearts perish!”-Holy Prophet(saws)<br><hr><br>\n<b>Perform Ghusl (Bath) </b><br>with the thought of washing away sins and as if its your last Ghusl.<br><hr><br><b>Fasting</b> is highly recommended on the day of 15th Shaban<hr>",
          "subtitle": "Recommended acts on 15th Shaaban"
        },
        {
          "title": "Concise Amaal",
          "color": "amber",
          "content": "<b>2 Rakah</b> Slaaat / Namaz<br> 1st Rakaat - Surah Al-hamd + Surah Kafiroon<br> 2nd Rakaat - Surah Al-Hamd + Surah Tawhid<br><hr><br>Tasbih of Fatima Zahra (sa)<br> Subhanallah (33 times)<br>Al-Humdolillah (33 times)<br>Allahhu Akbar (34 times)<br><hr><br>\n<a href=\"15-shaaban-salaat-after-isha-prayer.html\" class=\"group flex items-center justify-between px-3 py-2 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-lg hover:bg-emerald-50 dark:hover:bg-slate-700 transition-colors mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"font-medium text-slate-700 dark:text-emerald-400 group-hover:text-emerald-700 dark:group-hover:text-slate-200\">Dua by Imam Sadiq (as)</span>\n    <svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-slate-400 dark:text-emerald-400 group-hover:text-emerald-600 dark:group-hover:text-slate-500\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg>\n</a>\n<a href=\"15-shaban-dua-by-holy-prophet.html\" class=\"group flex items-center justify-between px-3 py-2 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-lg hover:bg-emerald-50 dark:hover:bg-slate-700 transition-colors mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"font-medium text-slate-700 dark:text-emerald-400 group-hover:text-emerald-700 dark:group-hover:text-slate-200\">Dua by Holy Prophet (sawa)</span>\n    <svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-slate-400 dark:text-emerald-400 group-hover:text-emerald-600 dark:group-hover:text-slate-500\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg>\n</a>\n<br><hr><br>\n<b>100 times 'Astaghfirullah' </b><br>with attention to seeking forgiveness.<br><hr><br><b>Tasbeehaatul Arbaa' 100 times</b><br><div dir=\"rtl\" class=\"font-arabic text-3xl md:text-4xl text-slate-800 text-center my-4\" style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">\nسُبْحَانَ اللهِ وَ الْحَمْدُ لِلهِ وَ لَا اِلٰهَ اِلَّا اللهُ وَ اللهُ اَكْبَر\n</div><br><hr>\n<a href=\"ziyarat-imam-hussain-night-15-shaban.html\" class=\"group flex items-center justify-between px-3 py-2 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-lg hover:bg-emerald-50 dark:hover:bg-slate-700 transition-colors mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"font-medium text-slate-700 dark:text-emerald-400 group-hover:text-emerald-700 dark:group-hover:text-slate-200\">Ziyarat of Imam Husain(as)</span>\n    <svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-slate-400 dark:text-emerald-400 group-hover:text-emerald-600 dark:group-hover:text-slate-500\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg>\n</a>",
